marketing: Shell Gadus S3 Wirerope T is a full EP lubricant developed for the lubrication and protection of open gears, wire ropes and sliding sufaces. The grease is based on high viscosity mineral oils, inorganic soap thickener and carefully selected additives to provide optimum performance.
